answers.body_markdown:
The `FastAdapter` Library tries to ensure listeners are implemented in the most efficient way possible. Reusing listeners and not re-creating them over and over again. It also tries to limit the potential of leaks. 

To do this the `FastAdapter` comes with a set of existing `Hooks` into your `RecyclerView` items.

A simple `ClickListener` to a item specific view can be done like this:

```kotlin
//just add an `EventHook` to your `FastAdapter` by implementing either a `ClickEventHook`, `LongClickEventHook`, `TouchEventHook`, `CustomEventHook`
fastAdapter.addEventHook(object : ClickEventHook&lt;SimpleImageItem&gt;() {
    override fun onBind(viewHolder: RecyclerView.ViewHolder): View? {
        //return the views on which you want to bind this event
        return if (viewHolder is SimpleImageItem.ViewHolder) {
            viewHolder.viewWhichReactsOnClick
        } else null
    }

    override fun onClick(v: View, position: Int, fastAdapter: FastAdapter&lt;SimpleImageItem&gt;, item: SimpleImageItem) {
        //react on the click event
    }
})
```

There are additional hooks for `LongClick`s, `TouchEvent`s and a generic interface to implement your own custom hooks. 

Starting with v4.1.0 the whole boilerplate can be simplified to:

```kotlin
adapter.addClickListener({ vh: SimpleImageItem.ViewHolder -&gt; vh.viewWhichReactsOnClick }) { _, position, _: FastAdapter&lt;SimpleImageItem&gt;, item: SimpleImageItem -&gt;
            //react on the click event
}
```

---- 

Source references: 

- [ClickEventHook][1]
- [LongClickEventHook][2]
- [TouchEventHook][3]
- [CustomEventHook][4]


  [1]: https://github.com/mikepenz/FastAdapter/blob/0dc139d5a93a0590884ba9ea1e792b677464607e/library-core/src/main/java/com/mikepenz/fastadapter/listeners/ClickEventHook.kt
  [2]: https://github.com/mikepenz/FastAdapter/blob/0dc139d5a93a0590884ba9ea1e792b677464607e/library-core/src/main/java/com/mikepenz/fastadapter/listeners/LongClickEventHook.kt
  [3]: https://github.com/mikepenz/FastAdapter/blob/0dc139d5a93a0590884ba9ea1e792b677464607e/library-core/src/main/java/com/mikepenz/fastadapter/listeners/TouchEventHook.kt
  [4]: https://github.com/mikepenz/FastAdapter/blob/0dc139d5a93a0590884ba9ea1e792b677464607e/library-core/src/main/java/com/mikepenz/fastadapter/listeners/CustomEventHook.kt

